 @{b}Extended painting tools@{ub}
        > Magic Stick (Pantograph)-function
        > Gradients as basic tool
        > Smear- and Blur-Tool
        > usual basic-tools
        > draw with fire

 @{b}integrated picture management with fxALBUM@{ub}
        > Fast catalogisation of pictures on your HD
        > directly linked with fxPAINT and therefore has
          optimal abilities for image manipulation
        > Printing of overviews
        > Organisation as catalogues
        > export as HTML-overviews

 @{b}integrated mini-converter fxCONV@{ub}
        > conversion of several dirs full of pictures with some clicks
        > conversion from any to any format supported by fxPAINT

 @{b}Completly new library of loader- and saver-modules@{ub}
        > highly optimized
        > read/write formats like ILBM, PCX, BMP, TARGA, JPEG, YUVN, LJPG,
          PNM, RGB8, TIFF, IFF24, ..
        > preview of the JPEG-fractures

 @{b}own GUI-System@{ub}
        > Realisation as BOOPSI-Objects
        > 24Bit GUI-elements and gradients
        > GUI contains many pictures
        > Bubble-Help for easy usage
        > three user-settable knownledge-degrees
        > automatic fixation of window-positions
        > GlowIcon-style
        > no hacks, patches, etc.

 @{b}ARexx-support@{ub}
        > connect fxPAINT with all your favourite programs!

 @{b}AmigaOS 3.5 system enhancement@{ub}
        > systemconform
        > allows fast overview of all your graphics
        > direct linking of Workbench and fxALBUM, fxCONV and fxCONV

 @{b}Full AmigaOS 3.5 support@{ub}
        > OS 3.5 icons
        > OS 3.5 printer support
        > OS 3.5 workbench support
        > OS 3.5 datatype support

 @{b}Internal modules@{ub}
        > fxALBUM
        > fxCONV
        > fxIMAGEMAP
        > fxPLUGINs


@{BG fill}@{FG shine}  Requirements@{FG text}@{BG back}
 @{b}Minimal@{ub}
        > AmigaOS 3.x
        > CPU: 68020
        > RAM: 6 MB
        > 10 MB harddisk

 @{b}Recommended@{ub}
        > AmigaOS 3.x
        > CPU: 68040/060
        > RAM: 16 MB
        > 10 MB harddisk or more

 @{b}Perfect@{ub}
        > AmigaOS 3.x
        > CPU: 68040/060 and PPC or even PPC-only
        > RAM: 32 MB or more
        > 20 MB harddisk or more


